item.title: babyarx
item.description: For this challenge we are given a .py file and the resulting hash. class baby_arx(): def __init__(self, key): assert len(key) == 64 self.state = list(key) def b(self): b1 = self.state[0] b2 = self.state[1] b1 = (b1 ^ ((b1 << 1) | (b1 & 1))) & 0xff b2 = (b2 ^ ((b2 >> 5) | (b2 << 3))) & 0xff b = (b1 + b2) % 256 self.
